# rotationMatrix

- _rotationMatrix(theta)_

Answers the 2×2 rotation matrix that rotates vectors counterclockwise by theta radians.

Counterclockwise rotation by 30°:

```
>>> (pi / 6).rotationMatrix
[
	[3.sqrt / 2, -1 / 2],
	[1 / 2, 3.sqrt / 2]
]
```

